entries.femaleVariant: I demand an immediate replacement vehicle. My car is broken. BRO-KEN, do you understand?
Yes, one hundred percent broken down. The battery is dead.
No, I won't check the fuel level, you imbecile! The car won't go because it won't even fucking start!
That's it, put a human being on the line. A complete moron, I don't care!
Anything but this-- this toaster equivalent of an AI!
